race.comment: UPWARDLY MOBILE (8) thereabouts of late at this level and gets the right tempo to finish over the top of these. Covered ground in the run and strong through the line when fourth over 1600m at Randwick. No excuses today in what looks an easier assignment. PHAROAHZANO (6) backmarker near his top for this, yet to place over the mile in two attempts. Returned good figures when a slashing fifth from back in the pack over 1400m at Randwick. Confident he will run the mile and no shock to see him race closer from the draw. SWEET TREATS (12) improving mare who deserves her chance here with the good record over the mile. Sharp weight drop with Nock's claim and can take a hand in the finish. NEXT PAY RUN (7) handy mare who scored a slick win over the 1400m at Grafton last time out. Should get the mile and goes into the exotics.
